{"tid":1508637,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【Twitter文宣】一定要有關鍵字＋TAG！希望大家一齊加入文宣","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T05:38:24.000Z","uid":308402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd79370e56607f381d78eab3f3985691eb6d063","tid":1508637,"uid":308402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"係twitter做文宣有呢三個重點，以下以英文做例子：<br />\n1. 一定要有關鍵字同TAG，唔好剩係圖同埋片，TAG最好係對應圖/片嘅，同埋多關鍵字/TAG出POST亦都可以幫助上Twitter Trending。<br />\n我個人覺得最好加返#HongKong #AntiELAB 依兩個TAG，因為外國人未必會知我地呢場運動嘅衍生議題：比如警暴。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">關鍵字可以用TAG代替！</span></strong><br />\n我依家係twitter主要見到以下嘅TAG：<br />\n#HongKong #HongKongProtests #HongKongProtesters #AntiELAB #StandwithHK #StandwithHongKong #PoliceBrutality #NoPoliceBrutality #BoycottMulan #Chinazi #Chinazism #BoycottChina<br />\n唔知文宣組手足可唔可以幫手係文宣圖加對應嘅TAG方便大家統一呢？<br />\n呢度都希望大家可以唔好濫用TAG，係果個內容先加返。<br />\n2. 文字內容原創！唔係人地以為係假ac/五毛ac﹗個人覺得錯少少grammar唔緊要嘅，最近要係你自己親身嘅表達﹗<br />\n3. 幫其他手足推POST Like/Retweet/Retweet with comment<br />\n<br />\n同埋大家自己可以定時PO返成個運動嘅成因係咩，比啲啱啱先關心嘅人知道呢場運動嘅前因後果同埋我地爭取緊咩。<br />\n<br />\n希望有手足分享下其他語言嘅TAG﹗大家可以幫手推﹗"},{"pid":"00e459e1c71894da9cd89860e800fac11d124645","tid":1508637,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=8d766f4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=e4763ae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/s